OL,3,CExclusive: Cumbrian MP suspended after
OL,4,Crebelling against 'family farm tax'
OL,6,FThe member of parliament for Penrith
OL,7,Fand Solway has been suspended as a
OL,8,FLabour MP.
OL,10,FMarkus Campbell-Savours voted against
OL,11,Fthe government over their plans to
OL,12,Fimpose inheritance tax on farmers.
OL,14,FHe was the only Labour MP to do so,
OL,15,Fthough a number of others raised
OL,16,Fconcerns and abstained on Tuesday
OL,17,Fevening.
OL,19,FThe vote related to the Budget, making
OL,20,Fhis rebellion more serious.
