OL,3,CExclusive: Cumbrian MP suspended after
OL,4,Crebelling against 'family farm tax'
OL,6,FDuring a debate in the House of
OL,7,FCommons, Mr Campbell-Savours said
OL,8,Fthere are 1,665 farms in his
OL,9,Fconstituency, and the policy would
OL,10,Fleave many farmers "devastated at the
OL,11,Fimpact on their family farms."
OL,13,FIn an interview with ITV Border on
OL,14,FWednesday afternoon, before we were
OL,15,Ftold the whip was being suspended, he
OL,16,Fsaid that Labour frontbench colleagues
OL,17,Fhad "reneged" on promises around
OL,18,Finheritance tax.
