OL,3,CExclusive: Cumbrian MP suspended after
OL,4,Crebelling against 'family farm tax'
OL,6,FPolitical Correspondent Tom Sheldrick
OL,7,Fspeaks to Markus Campbell-Savours MP
OL,8,Fabout his decision to rebel against
OL,9,Fthe government
OL,11,FAt their first Budget in October 2024,
OL,12,Fthe Labour government announced they
OL,13,Fwould impose inheritance tax on farm
OL,14,Fassets worth more than #1m from April
OL,15,F2026.
OL,17,FCritics have labelled it the 'family
OL,18,Ffarm tax'.
OL,20,FIt will apply at a 20% rate, half the
OL,21,Fnormal inheritance tax rate.
