OL,3,CExclusive: Cumbrian MP suspended after
OL,4,Crebelling against 'family farm tax'
OL,6,FChief Secretary to the Treasury James
OL,7,FMurray said during Tuesday's debate:
OL,8,F"The changes that we have set out to
OL,9,Fagricultural property relief are a
OL,10,Ffair way forward. They represent
OL,11,Fgenerous relief for people, while
OL,12,Fraising money for the public finances."
OL,14,FAt the Budget last week, the
OL,15,FChancellor announced that any of a #1m
OL,16,Fagricultural property relief and
OL,17,Fbusiness property relief allowance
OL,18,Fthat goes unused will be transferable
OL,19,Fbetween spouses and civil partners.
