OL,3,CExclusive: Cumbrian MP suspended after
OL,4,Crebelling against 'family farm tax'
OL,6,FNFU President Tom Bradshaw said: "this
OL,7,Fchange goes nowhere near far enough to
OL,8,Fremove the devastating impact of the
OL,9,Fpolicy on farming communities."
OL,11,FMPs voted in favour of the inheritance
OL,12,Ftax policy on Tuesday evening, by 327
OL,13,Fto 182.
OL,15,FMr Campbell-Savours will now sit as an
OL,16,Findependent MP.
OL,18,FIt is likely he will have the Labour
OL,19,Fwhip returned within a few months.
